    "breadcrumb": "WebLogic Kubernetes Toolkit UI",
    "content": "Before you begin Make sure you have read About the WKT UI Application .\nAbout the UI To help you understand how to use the WKT UI, we will step you through it, section by section, describing the important decisions to make and fields to populate. The sections are listed in the left side navigation pane.\nThe UI sections are:\nProject Settings Model Image Kubernetes Client Configuration WebLogic Operator WebLogic Domain Ingress Controller At the bottom of the page, the collapsed Console panel automatically appears and displays the stdout and stderr streams when running certain actions, such as Prepare Model.",
